casebody.data:
Aaron ISBY-ISRAEL, petitioner,
v.
Richard L. YOUNG, Judge, United States District Court for the Southern District of Indiana, et al. No. 13-10753. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 6, 2014.

Opinion

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
